---
type Props = {
  logoSrc?: string;
  logoAlt?: string;
  kicker?: string;
  title?: string;
  subtitle?: string;
};
---

<div class="card intro-card">
  <div class="kickstart-box">
    <div class="kickstart-grid">
      <div class="kickstart-left">
        <h1>GayJustice.org - KickStart - Oprichtingsfase</h1>
        <p class="intro-text">
          <strong>De eenmalige oprichtingskosten voor GayJustice.org.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="kickstart-date">
          <time datetime={new Date().toISOString()}>
            {new Date().toLocaleDateString('nl-NL', { 
              weekday: 'long', 
              year: 'numeric', 
              month: 'long', 
              day: 'numeric',
              hour: '2-digit',
              minute: '2-digit'
            })}
          </time>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-section">
      <h3>✅ - Terugbetaling van Kickstart-bijdragen</h3>
      <p>
        Kickstart-bijdragen worden terugbetaald door de stichting zodra en voor
        zover er reguliere donaties of andere inkomsten binnenkomen die deze
        oprichtingskosten dekken. <strong
          >Krijg een life-membership als Ere-lid van de Stichting.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>
      GayJustice.org bevindt zich in een initiële opbouwfase. In deze fase
      worden eenmalige kosten gemaakt voor juridische, organisatorische en
      technische inrichting.
    </p>

    <p>Deze kosten betreffen onder meer:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>notariële vastlegging;</strong></li>
      <li><strong>technische infrastructuur;</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <p class="cta-text">
      <a href="/steun/kickstart" class="kickstart-link"
        >Doneer met naam of anoniem via deze link.</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .card {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .intro-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .kickstart-box {
    background: white;
    border: 3px solid #000;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 22px;
    text-align: left;
    animation: dropIn 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes dropIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .kickstart-box h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e1b4b;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .kickstart-box h1 {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e1b4b;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .kickstart-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .kickstart-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .kickstart-date {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 2px solid #1e1b4b;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .kickstart-date time {
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .kickstart-box .intro-text {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .kickstart-box .highlight-section {
    background: rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid #1e1b4b;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .kickstart-box .highlight-section h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e1b4b;
  }

  .kickstart-box .highlight-section p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
  }

  .kickstart-box p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
  }

  .kickstart-box ul {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    padding-left: 24px;
    list-style-type: disc;
  }

  .kickstart-box li {
    margin: 8px 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
  }

  .kickstart-box .cta-text {
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .kickstart-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: #1e1b4b;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.3);
  }

  .kickstart-link:hover {
    background: #2d2653;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 860px) {
    .card {
      padding: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
